{
  "_id": "9mcYid7xJY9NiySx",
  "name": "Enlarge Spell",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/feats/enlarge-spell.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You can increase the range of your spells.</em><br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You can alter a spell with a range of close, medium, or long to increase its range by 100%. An enlarged spell with a range of close now has a range of 50 ft. + 5 ft./level, while medium-range spells have a range of 200 ft. + 20 ft./level and long-range spells have a range of 800 ft. + 80 ft./level. An enlarged spell uses up a spell slot one level higher than the spell's actual level.<br/><br/>Spells whose ranges are not defined by distance, as well as spells whose ranges are not close, medium, or long, do not benefit from this feat."
    },
